### Transactions API — Sample Requests
### Compatible with VS Code REST Client and JetBrains HTTP Client
### Start server first: bash demo/run.sh

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Task 1 – Core API
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1.1 Create deposit
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-AA001",
  "amount": 5000,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

###

### 1.2 Create deposit in EUR
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-AA001",
  "amount": 1200,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "type": "deposit"
}

###

### 1.3 Create withdrawal
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-AA001",
  "amount": 250.50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "withdrawal"
}

###

### 1.4 Create transfer
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-AA001",
  "toAccount": "ACC-BB002",
  "amount": 800,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

###

### 1.5 List all transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions

###

### 1.6 Get transaction by ID
# Copy an "id" value from the response above and paste it below
@txId = paste-transaction-id-here
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/{{txId}}

###

### 1.7 Get account balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-AA001/balance

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Task 2 – Validation (all return 400)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### 2.1 Invalid account format (should be ACC-XXXXX)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "acc-001",
  "amount": 100,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

###

### 2.2 Negative amount
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-AA001",
  "amount": -50,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

###

### 2.3 More than 2 decimal places
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-AA001",
  "amount": 99.999,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "deposit"
}

###

### 2.4 Invalid ISO 4217 currency code
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "ACC-AA001",
  "amount": 100,
  "currency": "XYZ",
  "type": "deposit"
}

###

### 2.5 Multiple validation errors at once
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "toAccount": "bad",
  "amount": -5.999,
  "currency": "ZZZ",
  "type": "deposit"
}

###

### 2.6 Transfer to same account
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-AA001",
  "toAccount": "ACC-AA001",
  "amount": 100,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Task 3 – Filtering
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### 3.1 Filter by account
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId=ACC-AA001

###

### 3.2 Filter by type
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?type=transfer

###

### 3.3 Filter by date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-06-30

###

### 3.4 Combined filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId=ACC-AA001&type=deposit&from=2026-01-01

###

### 3.5 Invalid filter — bad accountId format (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?accountId=bad-id

###

### 3.6 Invalid filter — from later than to (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?from=2026-12-31&to=2026-01-01

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Task 4A – Account Summary
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### 4A.1 Summary for ACC-AA001
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-AA001/summary

###

### 4A.2 Summary for ACC-BB002
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-BB002/summary

###

### 4A.3 Non-existent account (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-ZZ999/summary

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Task 4B – Simple Interest
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### 4B.1 5% annual rate for 30 days
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-AA001/interest?rate=0.05&days=30

###

### 4B.2 10% annual rate for 365 days
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-AA001/interest?rate=0.10&days=365

###

### 4B.3 Missing days parameter (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-AA001/interest?rate=0.05

###

### 4B.4 Negative rate (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts/ACC-AA001/interest?rate=-0.1&days=30

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Task 4C – CSV Export
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### 4C.1 Export all transactions as CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/export?format=csv

###

### 4C.2 Export only deposits as CSV
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/export?format=csv&type=deposit

###

### 4C.3 Export filtered by account and date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/export?format=csv&accountId=ACC-AA001&from=2026-01-01

###

### 4C.4 Unsupported format (400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions/export?format=xml

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Task 4D – Rate Limiting
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### 4D.1 Check rate limit headers in response
# Look at: X-RateLimit-Limit, X-RateLimit-Remaining, X-RateLimit-Reset
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions
